      "text": "Typically for each [[bounded context]] you will define a translation layer for each component with which you have to integrate that is outside the [[context map]]. Where integration is one-off, this approach of inserting a translation layer for each external system avoids corruption of the models with a minimum of cost. But when you find your subsystem in high demand, you may need a more flexible approach."
